    "body": "> AWS is not the only cloud provider module that can show in the prompt. Please run starship explain to confirm which is showing here.\r\n\r\nYou are right. It was the \"gcloud\" module. I have these configurations:\r\n- `~/.config/gcloud/active_config`: `default`\r\n- empty default configurations at `~/.config/gcloud/configurations/config_default`\r\n\r\nI have downloaded gcloud but have not actively used gcloud. It's not relevant to this bug report.",
