    "body": "To add to my previous comment, the behavior is the same, if you move credentials and config file to `$XDG_CONFIG_HOME/aws/` and export\n```fish\nset -x AWS_SHARED_CREDENTIALS_FILE \"$XDG_CONFIG_HOME\"\"/aws/credentials\"\nset -x AWS_CONFIG_FILE \"$XDG_CONFIG_HOME\"\"/aws/config\"\n```",
    "author_association": "NONE",
